high_descs: Turn right and move to the white table next to the door.
Pick up the tomato on the right-hand side of the table.
Turn left and go face the microwave to the left of the refrigerator.
Open the microwave, put the tomato inside, and heat the potato momentarily, then remove the tomato and shut the microwave.
Turn right and move to the white table again.
Place the heated tomato on the white table to the right of the wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Heat a whole tomato and place on the white table.

high_descs: Take a step to the right to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up the tomato on the counter.
Turn left and cross the room and turn right to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave and remove it.
Turn right and walk forward and turn left to face the white table.
Place the tomato on the white table.
anns.task_desc: To heat a tomato and return it to the table.

high_descs: Walk ahead and veer right to the right side of the table.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Turn left and walk ahead to the cabinet, then turn right and face the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn right and walk back to the white table on the other side of the fridge.
Place the tomato on the table to the right of the wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked tomato on a table.
